{"hash":"46cfa69c2391f66a55f0ae1f8a060cb3a6b05f71","data":{"post":{"id":"900b316f1bb94c1ff8ffc319f78651a2","title":"Generate color classes with scss","content":"<p>Lets be honest dealing with colors is a pain but things are simple when there are classes dedicated for colors and its also alot easy to remember as well like the way its being handled in tailwind css. So to generate such classes here is an scss function that does the job:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-scss\"><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$color</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token color\"><span class=\"token function\">rgb</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">141</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">3</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$color-name</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'grey'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">@for</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$i</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token number\">10</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">through</span> <span class=\"token selector\">100 </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">@if</span> <span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token variable\">$i</span> % 10 == 0 </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$percentage</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$i</span>*<span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token unit\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token keyword\">@if</span> <span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token variable\">$i</span> &lt; 50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$k</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">50</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$i</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//change the first value to lighten the whites i.e between 50 to 80</span>\n        <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$kper</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$k</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token unit\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token selector\">.<span class=\"token variable\">#{$color-name}</span>-<span class=\"token variable\">#{$i}</span> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n             <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">mix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token color\">white</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$kper</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> \n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">@else if</span> <span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token variable\">$i</span> == 50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token selector\">.<span class=\"token variable\">#{$color-name}</span>-<span class=\"token variable\">#{$i}</span> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token keyword\">@else if</span> <span class=\"token selector\"><span class=\"token variable\">$i</span> > 50</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$b</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$i</span> <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">35</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span><span class=\"token comment\">//change the second value to darken the blacks i.e between 20 to 50</span>\n      <span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$bper</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$b</span> <span class=\"token operator\">*</span> <span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token unit\">%</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token selector\">.<span class=\"token variable\">#{$color-name}</span>-<span class=\"token variable\">#{$i}</span> </span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          <span class=\"token property\">background-color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">mix</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token color\">black</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$color</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token variable\">$bper</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"usage\"><a href=\"#usage\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"icon icon-link\"></span></a>Usage</h4>\n<p>-Just put this function in a utility file that generates classes</p>\n<p>-Plug in the color and the color-name that maybe required</p>\n<p>-This can modified to be used to generate colors from an array</p>\n<p>-Here is a working example i have worked on <a href=\"https://codepen.io/ed613/pen/LYembWJ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Codepen</a>ðŸ‘ˆ</p>\n","date":"March 15, 2022","tags":[{"title":"frontend","path":"/tag/frontend/"},{"title":"scss","path":"/tag/scss/"},{"title":"css","path":"/tag/css/"}]}},"context":{}}